image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, page 5 of 51, for Donald J. Trump. The page lists positions held outside the United States Government in a tabular format. The table includes columns for organization name, location, organization type, position held, and the start and end dates of the position.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with form information, filer's name, and page number. The main body is a table with seven columns. A footer contains a note and a document identifier.
